        },
        "text_BctwwL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Dual-Action Collagen Support</strong></p><p>A powerful blend of collagen, Vitamin C, and citric acid helps strengthen the skin’s collagen structure from multiple layers — supporting smoother texture, reduced wrinkles, and a brighter, more refined complexion.</p><p><strong>Deep Hydration & Skin Barrier Defense</strong></p><p>With Hyaluronic Acid (HA) and Ceramide, the formula helps lock in moisture, calm inflammation, and reinforce the skin’s natural barrier — leaving skin softer, clearer, and more resilient against breakouts.</p><p><strong>Inside-Out Wellness Support</strong></p><p>Infused with 82 fermented plant extracts, The Pink supports digestion, gut health, and immunity — helping your body function better so your skin can reflect that healthy balance.</p><p><strong>Lean Beauty & Body Support</strong></p><p>Combining collagen and Vitamin C, the formula also supports firmer skin and a more toned appearance. With <strong>no sugar, no fat, and no acne-triggering ingredients</strong>, it’s designed for a clean, confident glow without compromise.</p><p><br/>EVERY INGREDIENT HAS A PURPOSE. EVERY BOTTLE IS A COMPLETE SYSTEM — NOT JUST A COLLAGEN DRINK.<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
