            "title": "What are the benefits of the 82 fermented plant extracts in The Pink product?",
            "content": "<p>They provide prebiotics and gut-friendly fiber, supporting a healthy digestive system and helping reduce the buildup of toxins in the gut. By balancing the gut microbiome, they also positively influence the skin’s microbiome — helping to minimize the causes of acne, inflammation, irritation, and redness.<br/></p>",
